benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: GET /1.0/kb/invoiceItems/{invoiceItemId}/customFields - Retrieve invoice item custom fields

covered: Valid Request: Scenarios include successful retrieval with valid invoiceItemId and proper data
Empty Response: Item with no custom fields returns an empty JSON array
Query Parameters: Variants including audit parameter handling and extra parameters are tested
gaps: Pagination: No tests cover pagination behavior for large datasets
Caching Behavior: No tests validate caching headers (ETag, Cache-Control)
Rate Limiting: No explicit rate-limiting tests; only concurrency/performance tests
Forbidden access (403): No tests validating insufficient permissions on valid auth
Backward compatibility: Not explicitly tested; older Accept header variations beyond TC14
recommendations: Add explicit pagination tests with limit/offset and verify proper pagination metadata
Add caching tests to verify ETag/Cache-Control headers and cache validation
Add explicit rate-limiting tests (429) and throttling scenarios under burst traffic
Add 403 Forbidden scenario to cover authenticated but unauthorized access
Add more comprehensive backward compatibility tests for header and response structure across API versions
